@startuml
[*] --> Created
Created --> Persisted : save in MongoDB
Persisted --> Streamed : publish SSE event
Persisted --> Unread : default is_read = false
Streamed --> Unread
Unread --> Read : mark read / read-all
Read --> Expired : TTL / expires_at reached
Unread --> Expired : TTL / expires_at reached
Expired --> [*]
@enduml
